OL,4,Cpost-Covid in UK, figures reveal
OL,6,FIn England, 14% of licensed premises
OL,7,Fclosed during the same period, while
OL,8,F12.6% closed in Scotland. The data is
OL,9,Fnot available for Northern Ireland.
OL,11,FThe figures from UKHospitality come
OL,12,Fbefore the Welsh government cuts
OL,13,Fbusiness rates relief in April - a
OL,14,Fdecision industry leaders are warning
OL,15,Fwill lead to more closures.
