OL,3,CWelsh hospitality sector hit hardest
OL,4,Cpost-Covid in UK, figures reveal
OL,6,FThe body has called for an extension
OL,7,Fto the business rates relief, but the
OL,8,FWelsh government says the policy was
OL,9,Fdesigned to be a temporary measure and
OL,10,Fthe money is needed to fund an
OL,11,Fincrease in funding for the NHS.
OL,13,FThe discount for retail, leisure and
OL,14,Fhospitality firms is set to be cut
OL,15,Ffrom 75% to 40% in the Welsh
OL,16,Fgovernment's budget, which is due to
OL,17,Fbe published next week. The rates
OL,18,Frelief for premises in England will
OL,19,Fremain at 75%.
