OL,4,Cpost-Covid in UK, figures reveal
OL,6,F"The stark numbers reflect the extent
OL,7,Fto which Welsh hospitality businesses
OL,8,Fhave suffered since the start of the
OL,9,Fpandemic.
OL,11,F"They will be concerning for our
OL,12,Fvenues and the thousands of
OL,13,Flivelihoods they support across Wales.
OL,15,F"We need immediate, increased business
OL,16,Frates support, followed by fast-track
OL,17,Freform, or more closures are
OL,18,Finevitable.
