OL,3,CWelsh hospitality sector hit hardest
OL,4,Cpost-Covid in UK, figures reveal
OL,6,F"UKHospitality Cymru and businesses
OL,7,Facross Wales are imploring the
OL,8,Fgovernment to change course on this
OL,9,Fissue, use the consequential payments
OL,10,Fawarded and restore the current level
OL,11,Fof 75% rates relief from April on.
OL,13,F"The survival of thousands of jobs and
OL,14,Flocal pubs and restaurants really does
OL,15,Fdepend on it."
OL,17,FFinance minister Rebecca Evans told
OL,18,FITV News the Welsh government already
OL,19,Fhad a "really generous system of
OL,20,Fsupport".
