OL,4,Cpost-Covid in UK, figures reveal
OL,6,FShe said: "Of course I understand the
OL,7,Ffrustrations and I know that business
OL,8,Fowners will understand the choices
OL,9,Fthat we've got to make as a Welsh
OL,10,Fgovernment.
OL,12,F"The NHS funding here in Wales will go
OL,13,Fup by 4% next year, but across the
OL,14,Fborder in England it's less than 1%.
OL,16,F"So we've made decisions consciously
OL,17,Fto prioritise the NHS and public
OL,18,Fservices through local government and
OL,19,FI do think that's a decision most
OL,20,Fpeople will understand."
